snippet.title: Super Mario Galaxy Multiplayer Split Screen Release
snippet.description:
RAM IS BEING PUSHED TO LIMITS, IF ON DOLPHIN TURN ON INCREASED MEMORY, IF ON WII DON'T OPEN A 100% SAVE FILE OR DO THINGS THAT TAKE A LOT OF RAM. I'LL BOTHER TO FIX RAM ISSUES LATER OR SOMETHING IDK.
Super Mario Galaxy True Multiplayer Split Screen Release. Files work with USA version only. All powerups work now. Gecko code is gecko code not AR code. Is compatible with Wii but don't ask me how to set it up, because I honestly don't know how. download here.
